                <p class="intro">The IUA publishes market standard policy wordings, manages statistical reporting for the company market segment, and represents company market interests alongside Lloyd's in market-wide initiatives including Blueprint Two (through the Joint London Initiative — JLI). For 991, candidates must understand that the London market is not synonymous with Lloyd's — the company market is a substantial separate segment, and the largest specialty risks are frequently placed across both segments simultaneously.</p>
